{
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "一键复制上一条命令到剪贴板 | Message Dump - A CLI tool to dump the last command output to the clipboard.",
    "homepage": "https://github.com/Cishoon/md",
    "license": {
        "identifier": "MIT"
    },
    "notes": [
        "This tool requires PowerShell 7+.",
        "Add the following line to your $PROFILE to enable it:",
        ". \"$(scoop prefix Cishoon.md)\\md.ps1\"",
        "",
        "If you want to use 'mdd' instead of 'md' (to avoid conflict with mkdir):",
        "$env:MD_CMD_NAME = 'mdd'; . \"$(scoop prefix Cishoon.md)\\md.ps1\""
    ],
    "notes_cn": [
        "此工具需要 PowerShell 7+。",
        "请将以下内容添加到您的 $PROFILE 中以启用它：",
        ". \"$(scoop prefix Cishoon.md)\\md.ps1\"",
        "",
        "如果您想使用 'mdd' 命令代替 'md' (避免与 mkdir 冲突)：",
        "$env:MD_CMD_NAME = 'mdd'; . \"$(scoop prefix Cishoon.md)\\md.ps1\""
    ],
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "url": "https://github.com/Cishoon/md/archive/refs/tags/v1.0.0.zip",
